name: Barcade
comment: Four single-stall bathrooms with no gender signage. Plus they have old arcade games, draft beer, and tacos.

name: Suncoast Church
directions: Through the door in the church
comment: It's open when the church is, and sometimes when the cafe is. You just have to ask. It is sort of associated with the school, so there are often kids around or functions on. If the actual church is closed, you might have to go down some stairs which makes it inaccessible.

name: Chick-fil-A
comment: I know that Chick-ful-A as a company has a bad rap. But I worked for this one for over 3 years and I transitioned during my time there. The owner operator and the entire staff was completely supportive of me and any LGBTQIA persons. In fact they have even helped my lgbtqia friends who also worked there or came in for food. I will continue to stand up for this establishment.
